"Dibuja una puerta lógica XOR de tres entradas, su función lógica y su tabla "
"de verdad."
msgstr ""
"Draw a logical gate of three entries, its logical function and its truth "
"table."


#: ../../source/electronic-gate-xor.rst:109
msgid ""
"Para realizar la tabla de verdad de la puerta recuerda que la salida vale "
"uno si los bits de entrada a uno son impares."
msgstr ""
"To perform the gate's truth table, remember that the exit is worth one if "
"the entrance bits are odd."
